{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你真能了解我么……","tone":"喃喃","chapter":14,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"嘿，真的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":108,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"说呀！说呀！你再不说，我就要生气了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"说呀，说呀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你真的要听？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"自是真的，否则我决不问你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"我平日虽然做出道貌岸然之态，但在风雪寒夜，四下无人时，只要有女子遇着我，便少不得被我摧残、蹂躏……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":142,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我为何要怕？我为何要逃？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"不怕？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你怎知我不会？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":166,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"我只是吓吓你的么？……","tone":"苦笑","chapter":14,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"不告而别？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"嗯，你溜了，溜了一夜，为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":190,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"昨夜乃是沈浪要我去办事的，难道他竟未告诉你？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"去追查一批人的下落。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":200,"line_end":200}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"他自己为何不去，却要你去？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"呀，不错，如今限期已到了……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":222,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"限期昨夜就到了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你越说我越不明白，究竟谁是代他赴约的人？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"展英松、方千里、胜滢……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"这其中的原故，我也不甚知晓，他只要我将这些人的行踪去向，探查明白，再回来相告……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":246,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"原来你们是约好了的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"约在什么时候？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":252,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"约定便在此刻。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"约在什么地方？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":256,"line_end":256},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"就在这里等。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":258,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"金兄眉毛一扬，我便来了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"此事说来话长……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":274,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"再长你也得说。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":276,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"我在见到那王夫人后，与她一夕长谈，她便将展英松、铁化鹤、方千里等人，俱都放了出来，我一来怕展英松、方千里等人，与你宿怨不解，二来与仁义庄约期已到，是以便请展、方等人，立刻赶到仁义庄去，将此中曲折说明，也免得我去了，此乃一举两得之事……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":278,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"这个，我知道，但你为何又要他去监视？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":280,"line_end":280},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"只因我始终觉得此事中还有蹊跷。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":282,"line_end":282},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"自然有些蹊跷，这我也知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":284,"line_end":284},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"你既知道，我便不必说了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你说，我偏要你说。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":288,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"是呀，这是为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"事后先见之明，你总是有的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你以为我真的糊涂么？我告诉你，她暗中必定还有阴谋，但行藏既已被你发现，便只有索性装作大方，将他们俱都放出……","tone":"调侃","chapter":14,"line_start":298,"line_end":298}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"你果然越来越聪明了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"哼","tone":"愤怒","chapter":14,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"这些事，我本无意瞒着你，但当着王怜花之面，我却不能向你说出……唉，幸好你在此遇着金兄，否则……否则……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"否则怎样？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":314,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"否则又要令人担心。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你会为我担心？鬼才相信哩……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"沈浪失声道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"多谢金兄……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"多谢两字，似乎不应自你口中向我说出。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"不错，这两字委实太俗。","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"金兄此后行止，又待如何？","tone":"犹豫","chapter":14,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"回去？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"不错，那柴玉关虽凶虽恶，但他待我之恩情不可谓不厚，终我一生，总是万万不能背弃于他……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"人以国士待我，我以国士报人，但……","tone":"喃喃","chapter":14,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"如此便好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":362,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"多多珍重……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":366,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"不错，是该走了。江湖险恶，奸人环伺，沈兄你……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_shen_lang","speaker_name":"沈浪","listener":null,"text":"金兄只管放心，我自会留意的，只是金兄你……","tone":"认真","chapter":14,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"但将血泪酬知己，生死又何妨……","tone":"微笑","chapter":14,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你还有什么话说？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我……我要跟着你走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"慢些，等我一等……带着我走……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":398,"line_end":398}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":401,"line_end":500,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"好，姓沈的，你不拉我，看我真的死了，你对不对得住你的良心，但……但我为什么不死呢……为什么不死呢……","tone":"喃喃","chapter":14,"line_start":418,"line_end":418},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"你真的跟来了……你何苦来呢？","tone":"无奈","chapter":14,"line_start":434,"line_end":434},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"从此你永远都要跟着我？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":440,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"可怜的孩子……","tone":"苦笑","chapter":14,"line_start":446,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"可怜的孩子……","tone":"喃喃","chapter":14,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你又何苦为了要气沈浪而跟着我？你又何苦……","tone":"无奈","chapter":14,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我不是为了沈浪，自己愿意跟着你的。","tone":"认真","chapter":14,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"但沈浪来追你回去如何？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我睬都不睬他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"真的？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":466,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"一千个真的，一万个真的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":468,"line_end":468},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你瞧，沈浪果然追来了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":470,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"在哪里？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":472,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"他来了我也不睬他，我……我……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":478,"line_end":478},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"我不回去，我死也不回去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":484,"line_end":484},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"但你又怎能真的跟着我？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你不让我跟着你，我就死在你面前。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你说什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":500,"line_end":500}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":501,"line_end":600,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"我说……你要跟着我，唉，就走吧。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":502,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你瞧，别人都怕你，我好得意。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":514,"line_end":514},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你得意什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":516,"line_end":516},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"你此刻便吃得下么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":526,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"到了","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":556,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"游魂","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":556,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"此地生意太好……","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":558,"line_end":558},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"生意好的地方，酒菜必定不差。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":560,"line_end":560},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"怎奈座无虚席。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":562,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"无妨，你跟着我来吧。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":564,"line_end":564},{"speaker":"char_jin_wu_wang","speaker_name":"金无望","listener":null,"text":"果然有你的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":572,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"这就叫做狐假虎威。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"你为何不笑了？我喜欢你笑的模样。","tone":"陈述","chapter":14,"line_start":578,"line_end":578},{"speaker":"char_zhu_qi_qi","speaker_name":"朱七七","listener":null,"text":"噗","tone"